1
00:00:20,941 --> 00:00:21,983
You alive?

2
00:00:22,692 --> 00:00:23,735
Working late?

3
00:00:24,444 --> 00:00:25,487
Yeah

4
00:00:28,573 --> 00:00:30,033
Poor you

5
00:00:30,033 --> 00:00:31,743
Just go home and have a beer

6
00:00:31,743 --> 00:00:32,619
Hang in there

7
00:00:33,912 --> 00:00:34,871
Yeah

8
00:01:10,991 --> 00:01:12,075
Welcome

9
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:17,622
Need a bag?

10
00:01:18,206 --> 00:01:19,290
No

11
00:01:21,501 --> 00:01:22,794
Ex.. Excuse me

12
00:02:37,744 --> 00:02:39,287
How about a blind date this weekend?

13
00:02:40,622 --> 00:02:42,415
He's a guy from my college major

14
00:02:42,415 --> 00:02:43,458
He's a civil servant

15
00:02:45,126 --> 00:02:46,294
Forget it

16
00:02:47,212 --> 00:02:47,962
Why?

17
00:02:49,589 --> 00:02:50,840
I'm tired

18
00:02:51,716 --> 00:02:53,259
Are you tired every day?

19
00:02:55,303 --> 00:02:56,262
Yeah

20
00:02:57,889 --> 00:03:00,350
So, you won't meet him?

21
00:03:01,059 --> 00:03:02,560
Yeah

22
00:03:03,061 --> 00:03:05,313
Seriously, Kim Sohee

23
00:03:26,584 --> 00:03:27,710
Hey

24
00:03:27,710 --> 00:03:28,837
Yesterday on Netflix

25
00:03:28,837 --> 00:03:30,046
I watched a GL drama

26
00:03:30,046 --> 00:03:31,256
What?

27
00:03:31,256 --> 00:03:33,883
What was it? Yuri?

28
00:03:33,883 --> 00:03:34,926
Anyway

29
00:03:34,926 --> 00:03:37,053
Man, it really made my heart flutter

30
00:03:38,096 --> 00:03:39,389
Eat your food

31
00:03:40,557 --> 00:03:43,059
What do you even do for fun?

32
00:03:43,810 --> 00:03:45,061
Nothing's fun

33
00:03:45,228 --> 00:03:46,563
Yeah, I know

34
00:03:47,814 --> 00:03:50,233
Just go on a blind date or something

35
00:03:50,859 --> 00:03:51,734
Hey

36
00:03:52,068 --> 00:03:53,820
I'm just tired of men

37
00:03:53,820 --> 00:03:56,030
It's not that I don't want to date

38
00:03:58,158 --> 00:04:00,201
You're tired of men?

39
00:04:06,249 --> 00:04:07,208
Forget it, whatever

40
00:04:09,252 --> 00:04:11,254
What time do you get off today?

41
00:04:11,254 --> 00:04:12,130
Me?

42
00:04:12,130 --> 00:04:13,882
At 6, you?

43
00:04:14,465 --> 00:04:15,300
Me?

44
00:04:15,300 --> 00:04:16,176
10?

45
00:04:16,926 --> 00:04:18,011
Again?

46
00:04:18,636 --> 00:04:20,263
My manager is crazy

47
00:04:21,556 --> 00:04:22,807
Wow, that sounds awful

48
00:04:23,183 --> 00:04:24,184
It's fine, at the convenience store

49
00:04:24,184 --> 00:04:25,810
I can just have a can of beer

50
00:04:27,604 --> 00:04:30,106
Stop being pathetic and drinking alone

51
00:04:30,106 --> 00:04:31,983
You need to meet a guy to drink with

52
00:04:32,483 --> 00:04:34,319
Hey, the college friend I mentioned

53
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:35,528
I'm telling you he's great

54
00:04:35,528 --> 00:04:36,279
The one who's a civil servant..

55
00:04:40,450 --> 00:04:41,659
Just eat

56
00:04:44,495 --> 00:04:45,622
Ouch!

57
00:05:07,310 --> 00:05:08,186
Excuse me

58
00:05:18,613 --> 00:05:21,115
This was the last one so I saved it

59
00:05:25,995 --> 00:05:27,038
For me?

60
00:05:29,207 --> 00:05:30,917
Since you buy the same thing every day

61
00:05:36,005 --> 00:05:37,507
Thank you

62
00:05:38,424 --> 00:05:40,718
Not buying Chips Ahoy?

63
00:05:41,761 --> 00:05:42,971
Ah...

64
00:05:49,394 --> 00:05:51,062
You have a good memory

65
00:05:51,062 --> 00:05:52,522
Someone buying the same thing every day

66
00:05:52,522 --> 00:05:53,940
Shouldn't be that common

67
00:05:55,024 --> 00:05:56,067
No

68
00:05:56,484 --> 00:05:57,443
There are a lot

69
00:05:59,529 --> 00:06:00,571
Really?

70
00:06:02,407 --> 00:06:04,284
But..

71
00:06:04,284 --> 00:06:07,203
No one else drops their ID card

72
00:06:19,549 --> 00:06:21,551
That's 4,900 won

73
00:06:26,889 --> 00:06:29,225
It says insufficient funds

74
00:06:33,479 --> 00:06:35,106
Just a moment

75
00:06:43,948 --> 00:06:45,408
This too..

76
00:06:47,201 --> 00:06:48,578
This one doesn't work either?

77
00:06:50,455 --> 00:06:52,957
Then with my phone..

78
00:06:58,421 --> 00:07:00,715
Crazy..

79
00:07:07,555 --> 00:07:08,348
Huh?

80
00:07:08,348 --> 00:07:10,391
Oh, please don't do that

81
00:07:12,810 --> 00:07:13,853
Just take it

82
00:07:16,022 --> 00:07:17,690
But still

83
00:07:20,985 --> 00:07:22,695
Ms. Kim Sohee

84
00:07:23,321 --> 00:07:25,490
You work at Cheongrim Planning?

85
00:07:32,413 --> 00:07:34,415
You work close by

86
00:07:42,423 --> 00:07:44,634
Just pay me next time you come

87
00:07:50,139 --> 00:07:51,557
Thank you

88
00:08:17,917 --> 00:08:20,920
Hey, you really skipping the blind date?

89
00:08:21,546 --> 00:08:23,256
I'm telling you he's great

90
00:08:23,673 --> 00:08:25,174
Should I send you a picture?

91
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:42,233
I'll think about it

92
00:08:43,901 --> 00:08:46,237
Oh, what? Really?

93
00:09:13,431 --> 00:09:15,266
Hey, talk to her

94
00:09:16,601 --> 00:09:19,645
Excuse me, do you have a boyfriend?

95
00:09:20,438 --> 00:09:21,772
Need a bag?

96
00:09:22,940 --> 00:09:24,484
Oh, yes..

97
00:09:24,484 --> 00:09:26,652
My friend is a bit shy

98
00:09:27,069 --> 00:09:28,446
This is his number

99
00:09:29,322 --> 00:09:31,282
Please just give him a call

100
00:09:58,267 --> 00:10:00,061
Paying my tab from yesterday

101
00:10:04,649 --> 00:10:05,983
Thank you

102
00:10:10,530 --> 00:10:12,657
This too?

103
00:10:13,950 --> 00:10:16,244
Oh, this is..

104
00:10:18,496 --> 00:10:20,081
For you, Jieun

105
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:23,501
What?

106
00:10:25,878 --> 00:10:28,339
A late-night snack for my tab

107
00:10:30,424 --> 00:10:31,384
Oh, I'm fine..

108
00:10:31,384 --> 00:10:32,885
If you don't want to eat it

109
00:10:32,885 --> 00:10:34,136
Just throw it away

110
00:10:34,595 --> 00:10:35,680
You can throw it away

111
00:10:45,189 --> 00:10:49,569
[For the ID, beer & tab! Enjoy! -Sohee Kakao:SFL0519]
